expect(svg.style.minWidth).toBe("460px");  // Direct property access for edge cases
```

**Pattern 6: CSS Attribute Selection**
```typescript
// From PriceChart.test.tsx (line 77-78)
expect(paths[0]).toHaveAttribute("stroke", getOutcomeColor(0));
expect(circles[i]).toHaveAttribute("fill", getOutcomeColor(1));
```

